Apple Watch or iPhone  - it’s your choice now.
Go as pro, be your own hero.


- Control your action camera on distance up to 20m (65ft);
- Save your camera power using bluetooth only;
- Automatic connection;
- Mode change;
- Shooting;
- Works without your iPhone, complete independent using just your Apple Watch;


Limitations:
- Doesn't support old models 4th generation and lower;
- Several issues connected with hardware synchronization still possible: there are multiple camera models and different firmwares for each of model.

If you have any idea or request don't hesitate to write us:
http://goremo.me/support

*Сompatible devices: iPhone 13 Pro Max, 13 Pro, 13, 13 mini, 12 Pro Max, 12 Pro, 12, 12 mini, 11 Pro Max, 11 Pro, 11, Xs Max, Xs and Xr.

Camera FrontBack transforms your iPhone into a multi-cam allowing you to capture video from two cameras at the same time.

With our video App, we want people around the world to shoot amazing views, architecture, pets, and friends and at the same time allow them to express their emotions being on one screen. Try and get surprised at how you reacted to something which was important to you at the moment.

Features:
◆ Picture-in-picture (PIP);
◆ Simultaneous work with front and rear cameras;
◆ Animates in real-time;
◆ Circle mode;
◆ Oval mode;
◆ Square mode;
◆ Full-Screen mode;
◆ Split-screen mode;
◆ Pinch-to-zoom;
◆ Capture moment;
◆ Moveable around screen;

it has a user-friendly interface and it's easy to use.
